{"tid":194536,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"朱千雪淡定獻唱獲盛讚賦歌唱天份 抱恙簡淑兒底聲音樂搭夠","createTime":"2017-04-10T04:53:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T06:25:55.000Z","uid":9573,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e9958ef70ed9178b932de70c8225e74cab8124ce","tid":194536,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T04:53:24.000Z","msg":"朱千雪與簡淑兒昨日出席尖沙嘴商場騷，兩人同展歌喉，第二次公開獻唱的千雪表現淡定，還被讚唱歌好聽，唱功絕不遜於時下歌手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GnIRN41sU8ERRrLc_DoCIg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20170409f175351.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FGnIRN41sU8ERRrLc_DoCIg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20170409f175351.jpg&h=b48fddf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n問千雪想唱歌嗎？她說：「想呀，唱劇集主題曲，但公司未發掘到，希望遲啲唱插曲先。」復活節學校放假，但她要應付考試未能放鬆，直至暑假都只會拍一些節目，未能入劇組。簡淑兒跟張衞健同劇演出，她說：「劇本只係畀佢參考，佢完全將角色私有化，改劇本都係令劇本更好笑，事前會幫大家度埋對白，我哋只係怕忍唔到笑。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://images.performgroup.com/di/library/omnisport/56/1c/antonio-conte_5lxbwqv30hv91juecedwu3uma.jpg?t=1324374091&amp;w=460&amp;h=320\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.performgroup.com%2Fdi%2Flibrary%2Fomnisport%2F56%2F1c%2Fantonio-conte_5lxbwqv30hv91juecedwu3uma.jpg%3Ft%3D1324374091%26w%3D460%26h%3D320&h=6c48b9b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n而首次單飛獻唱的簡淑兒，因聲帶發炎未康復，公司為免她中途失聲，安排有襯底人聲的音樂伴奏。簡淑兒表現較為緊張，她解釋因首次獨唱，加上之前聲帶發炎及感冒未清，為免失準選擇用有底聲的音樂。她說拍《大帥哥》大家好驚被傳染感冒，見到她便彈開。她又大讚張衛健將個人風格加入角色，令角色更生動；並謂對方改對白前會對戲，其他演員都接得上。"},{"pid":"566fac064f8a0ecab2cf7ad59b983e9e82f079b2","tid":194536,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:29:02.000Z","msg":"真係相形見絀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"853103a880f00e557530ef12ea7a2509a236964c","tid":194536,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:37:46.000Z","msg":"正評比干地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81a0c983ef52ae062c10c9f06e1e54d4cec6ff54","tid":194536,"uid":33176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:40:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係相形見絀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n簡淑兒式'處刑技'<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54410a070b9e8d4331400f15ab71dd37c786a771","tid":194536,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:41:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正評比干地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93685cfd59f504e62340603faddaeaa5ef35c738","tid":194536,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T06:07:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c09351d7839625d4d39c3a383d660deffec885a","tid":194536,"uid":30459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T06:11:14.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩出雙飛人廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f290fc382af056fd95fd8be0a6bb0ea2da1757f","tid":194536,"uid":4241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T06:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}